## Rugby union in Ireland

[Ulster](/Ulster_Rugby) (white) vs. [Leinster](/Leinster_Rugby) (blue) in the [2012 Heineken Cup Final](/2012_Heineken_Cup_Final).
Country Ireland Governing body [Irish Rugby Football Union](/Irish_Rugby_Football_Union) National team [Ireland](/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team) First played 1869, [Dublin](/Dublin) Registered players 90,209 &#91;1&#93; Clubs 56 clubs affiliated to the [Ulster](/Ulster) Branch
